    <decisions>
        <name>Copy_1_of_Combined_or_Brand_New_Program_Path</name>
        <label>Onboarding Path?</label>
        <locationX>506</locationX>
        <locationY>276</locationY>
        <defaultConnectorLabel>Default Outcome</defaultConnectorLabel>
        <rules>
            <name>Spanish_Preferred_Language</name>
            <conditionLogic>1 AND (2 OR 3)</conditionLogic>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>$Record.Account__r.Related_Payer_Customer_Type__c</leftValueReference>
                <operator>EqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <stringValue>Government Payer</stringValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>$Record.Preferred_Language__c</leftValueReference>
                <operator>EqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <stringValue>Spanish</stringValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>$Record.Onboarding_Path__c</leftValueReference>
                <operator>EqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <stringValue>Gov Group Training</stringValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <connector>
                <targetReference>Assign_Spanish_Preferred_Language_OBS</targetReference>
            </connector>
            <label>Spanish Preferred Language</label>
        </rules>
        <rules>
            <name>Combined_Self_Serve_GOV</name>
            <conditionLogic>1 AND (2 OR 3)</conditionLogic>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>$Record.Account__r.Related_Payer_Customer_Type__c</leftValueReference>
                <operator>EqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <stringValue>Government Payer</stringValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>$Record.Onboarding_Path__c</leftValueReference>
                <operator>EqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <stringValue>Combined</stringValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>$Record.Onboarding_Path__c</leftValueReference>
                <operator>EqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <stringValue>Self Serve</stringValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <connector>
                <targetReference>Assign_Combined_GOV_OBS</targetReference>
            </connector>
            <label>Combined/Self Serve GOV</label>
        </rules>
        <rules>
            <name>Copy_1_of_Combined_Path</name>
            <conditionLogic>and</conditionLogic>
            <conditions>
                <leftValueReference>$Record.Onboarding_Path__c</leftValueReference>
                <operator>EqualTo</operator>
                <rightValue>
                    <stringValue>Combined</stringValue>
                </rightValue>
            </conditions>
            <connector>
                <targetReference>Assign_Combined_OBS_RR</targetReference>
            </connector>
            <label>Combined Path</label>
        </rules>
    </decisions>
    <description>When new combined funnels are created with owner combined funnel queue, this flow assigns those with onboarding path combined and brand new program. Updated 6/26/23: added 2 additional routing paths for government licensees
6/11/24: added criteria to assign BNP site adds
12/4/24: removed BNP path since reps are required to enter the OBS at the time of CW after they book the BNP intro call in CP</description>
